    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Pharmacyclics LLC.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find out about the safety of adding the investigational drug
      motexafin gadolinium to a standard course of chemotherapy with temozolomide for patients with
      malignant glioma. Secondly, the study will determine how many patients will respond to this
      treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
